Option 2: Discard snapshot changes (rollback)
Use if you want to restore original state
1. Ensure VM is off:

# virsh shutdown alpine1

2. Edit XML:
# virsh edit alpine1

Replace:

<source file='/var/lib/libvirt/images/alpine1-snap-20260427.qcow2'/>

With:

<source file='/var/lib/libvirt/images/alpine1.qcow2'/>

3. Remove entire backingStore section:

Delete:

<backingStore type='file'>
  <format type='qcow2'/>
  <source file='/var/lib/libvirt/images/alpine1.qcow2'/>
</backingStore>

4. Delete overlay:
rm -f /var/lib/libvirt/images/alpine1-snap-20260427.qcow2

